Class Passenger

  • java.lang.Object
    • carpooling_package.Passenger
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PassengerFunctionalities
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    SubscriberPassenger, UnsubscriberPassenger

    public abstract class Passenger
extends java.lang.Object
implements PassengerFunctionalities
    This abstract class have almost all the functions that a passenger can do, and it holds all the data of the passenger, including his information, his trips, if he is a subscriber or not, and all the reviews and complains he has submitted
